    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is marinating, preheat the grill to high</p><p>Grate your <strong>beetroot </strong>then add<strong> </strong>to a sieve over the sink and squeeze out any excess water</p><p>Top, tail and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and slice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Strip your<strong> mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p>",
