    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>marinated chicken breast </strong>to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray under the grill for 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and starting to char – this is your <strong>tandoori chicken breast</strong></p>",
