    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add the <strong>grated beetroot</strong> and<strong> carrot</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>,<strong> sultanas</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar</strong>, the <strong>remaining ginger paste</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped mint </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), 1/2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>beetroot & carrot slaw</strong></p>",
