      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is nearly cooked, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan over a medium-high heat</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>roti </strong>with a little <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the roti to the pan and cook for 1-2 min on each side or until warmed through</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to do this in batches or use a second pan!</p>",
