      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, spread the<strong> mango yoghurt</strong> over the<strong> warmed roti </strong>then top with some<strong> beetroot & carrot slaw </strong>and <strong>tandoori chicken breast</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped mint</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> remaining beetroot & carrot slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
